short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Catch Trello links and open in "Trello External Window" application.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension works for "Trello External Window" application. It's catching new tabs in browser with links like trello.com/c/123abc and send it to application. Works only with links to boards and cards.
